ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectLoran-A Station Gray Point BC 1971 Termination of Treaty (US) # 6
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to terminate for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between Canada and the United States of America relating to the Construction and Maintenance by Canada of a Loran-A Station at Gray Point, British Columbia, done on 8 April 1971.
